  {
    "name": "ED - Units by Army Type",
    "civilopediaText": [
      {
        "text": "Military units in Emperors and Deities are categorized into five army types: 'Levy Army', 'Standing Army', 'Noble Army', 'Mercenary Army', and 'Barbaric Army'. Each type has different recruitment methods, maintenance costs, and strategic roles. Below is a list of units grouped by their primary army tag.",
        "header": 3
      },
      {
        "separator": true
      },
      {
        "text": "'Levy Army'",
        "header": 4
      },
      {
